#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/behavior.phtml:23
msgid "Behavior"
msgstr "Åtferd"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:23
msgid "Colors"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/colors.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Colors the person boxes by family branch. Each couple shares the same color, "
"derived from the chosen base colors."
msgstr ""
"Fargar personboksane etter familiegrein. Kvart par deler same farge, avleidd "
"frå dei valde basisfargane."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:25
msgid "Control panel"
msgstr "Kontrollpanel"

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/config.phtml:97
msgid ""
"Controls which name part shrinks first when a box is too narrow for the full "
"name. \"Automatic\" uses the tree's surname tradition (Icelandic abbreviates "
"surnames; everything else abbreviates given names)."
msgstr ""
"Styrer kva for ein namnedel som vert forkorta først når ein boks er for smal "
"for heile namnet. «Automatisk» brukar etternamnstradisjonen til treet "
"(islandsk forkortar etternamn; alt anna forkortar førenamn)."

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:23
msgid "Details"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/modules/pedigree-chart/form/details.phtml:34
msgid ""
"Displays a person's alternate name, if available. This simultaneously "
"enlarges the individuals' respective boxes to create the necessary space for "
"the display."
msgstr ""
"Syner alternativt namn på personar der dette er tilgjengeleg. Dette vil og "
"utvide personboksar for å gi plass til syninga."

#: resources/views/modules/components/buttonbar/png-export-button.phtml:18
